<DOC><DOCNO> ZF32-026-138 </DOCNO><DOCID>11 452 270</DOCID><JOURNAL>MacWEEK  Oct 29 1991 v5 n37 p20(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Coastal Associates Publishing L.P. 1991.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Candela palette of programs aids CMYK work and color calibration.andO;(Candela Ltd.'s Candela434, 4-SEPS, Sys-Cal and Print-Calcolor-transformation software packages for cyan, magenta, yellow,black color) (product announcement)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Said, Carolyn.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Candela Ltd. (Product introduction).andO;Product:   Candela434 (Computer graphics software) (Product introduction)4-SEPS (Computer graphics software) (Product introduction)Sys-Cal (Image processing software) (Product introduction)Print-Cal (Printer software) (Product introduction).andO;Topic:     ColorGraphics SoftwareData ConversionImage ProcessingSoftware PackagesPrinter Software.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>By Carolyn SaidandM;Minneapolis -- Candela Ltd. recently shipped a quartet ofcolor-transformation software products aimed at high-end users and systemsintegrators.andM;andgt;Candela434, priced at $5,000, offers &quot;round-trip&quot; conversion from CMYK(cyan, magenta, yellow, black) to RGB (red, green, blue) and back again.andP;  Itis designed for desktop publishers and artists who scan in images in CMYK,manipulate them on screen in RGB, and then output them as process separationsin CMYK.andM;Candela434 would not be needed by users who exclusively use the new CMYKediting modes of image-manipulation programs such as Adobe Photoshop 2.0 andLetraset's ColorStudio 1.5, Candela said.andM;andgt;4-SEPS, priced at $2,500, converts RGB images to CMYK data for colorseparation.andP;  Also targeted at high-end desktop publishers, 4-SEPS providescontrols over variables such as GCR (gray component replacement), UCR(undercolor removal), dot gain and black point.andM;Candela434 and 4-SEPS offer conversions five times more accurate than thoseof competing products, said John Grimald, Candela president.andM;andgt;Sys-Cal, priced at $5,000, is an end-to-end system that provides calibrationbetween a color-film scanner and a color-film recorder.andM;andgt;Print-Cal, priced at $2,500, lets users accurately profile outputcharacteristics of color printers and build custom look-up tables of colorvalues.andM;Candela Ltd. is at 9206 12th Ave.andP;  S., Minneapolis, Minn.andP;  55425.andP;  Phone(612) 885-9077; fax (612) 888-6916.andO;</TEXT></DOC>